{"tid":1411200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我支持一帶一路及大灣區政策","createTime":"2019-08-05T03:09:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-15T09:48:53.000Z","uid":82033,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"ff61a59afcb93e9bb4c3b412d4523e5e444c5a7e","tid":1411200,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:09:40.000Z","msg":"我係一個愛國愛港嘅藍絲<br />\n本地大學畢業，從事香港最大產業之一<br />\n<br />\n香港在國家政策的角色<br />\n係金融、保險、專業服務(e.g. Accounting)<br />\n<br />\n波叔講果啲「受影響」行業從來都係小眾<br />\n香港應該守護政制及法律自由穩定<br />\n因自由選舉及政府取態會大大影響Sovereign Rating<br />\n<br />\n所以，請政府立即回應社會真正經濟貢獻者嘅訴求<br />\n而唔係再偏頗小眾(包括新移民、非主要產業、退休及非居港人士）<br />\n<br />\n利申：我認真，無曲"},{"pid":"ea0d10f54ae17a3784e5f019349af23ba811f66f","tid":1411200,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:13:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2d7232282ca7ef5ca0878fe2ef506ecb1ec6f8cd","tid":1411200,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:13:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2b1a0ed141633313d147600e456b79f937009b41","tid":1411200,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:19:51.000Z","msg":"自推希望有人睇到<br />\n希望黃絲都可以聽聽有用腦嘅藍絲諗乜"},{"pid":"7569713c39d95acffa1b599b874a03076b8b7a21","tid":1411200,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:23:36.000Z","msg":"自推希望有人睇到<br />\n希望黃絲都可以聽聽有用腦嘅藍絲諗乜"},{"pid":"8c967ab4187cf14e852de08c5460c018c410452c","tid":1411200,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T03:53:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"380a70dfd8811c2f185ca632bde19995edfde590","tid":1411200,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T04:21:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"89ac7f46a9e324904d8c41282ad3c4fb89846ea1","tid":1411200,"uid":82033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T09:04:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"50ecb614d0a98153cf31a2ec593a7ca21749a123","tid":1411200,"uid":82033,"like":0,"disli